          <title>Miramonte rallies from early deficit, defeats Hayward to capture NCS D4 title</title>
          <description><![CDATA[HAYWARD — Adversity had become such a constant companion for Miramonte this season that Saturday night’s trouble felt more familiar than frightening.  The Matadors had already weathered a season of injuries, departures and a tired perception that kids from Orinda can’t take a hit and give one too.]]></description>
